trans-unit.source: Specifies constants that define the location in the project to insert a property.
trans-unit.target: Anger konstanter som definierar platsen i projektet för att infoga en egenskap.

trans-unit.source: Replace the existing [Property](../Topic/Property%20Element%20\(MSBuild\).md) element if it exists.
trans-unit.target: Ersätta den befintliga [egenskapen](../Topic/Property%20Element%20\(MSBuild\).md) element om den finns.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, create the `Property` after the last [Import](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Annars skapar du den `Property` efter senast [importera](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element i projektet.

trans-unit.source: Replace the existing [Property](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element if it exists.
trans-unit.target: Ersätta den befintliga [egenskapen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element om den finns.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, if possible, create a new `Property` element as a child of an existing compatible [PropertyGroup](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Annars, om möjligt, skapa en ny `Property` element som underordnad till en befintlig kompatibel [PropertyGroup](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.

trans-unit.source: If necessary, create a new compatible `PropertyGroup` element immediately following the last `PropertyGroup` in the project.
trans-unit.target: Vid behov kan du skapa en ny kompatibel `PropertyGroup` omedelbart efter sist elementet `PropertyGroup` i projektet.
